OL,3,CDrug-related deaths in Wales increases
OL,4,Cyear-on-year
OL,6,FDrug-related deaths have hit a new
OL,7,Frecord high, with the number involving
OL,8,Fa powerful synthetic opioid almost
OL,9,Fquadrupling, according to official
OL,10,Ffigures,
OL,12,FThere were 5,565 deaths related to
OL,13,Fdrug poisoning registered in England
OL,14,Fand Wales last year, the Office for
OL,15,FNational Statistics said.
OL,17,FOf those, 417 drug-related deaths were
OL,18,Fregistered in Wales - an increase from
OL,19,F377 the previous year.
