OL,6,FA total of 195 deaths registered last
OL,7,Fyear involved nitazenes, a figure
OL,8,Falmost four times that of the 52
OL,9,Fdeaths registered in 2023.
OL,11,FThese substances can be 100 times more
OL,12,Fpotent than heroin and bring a high
OL,13,Frisk of overdose.
OL,15,FThe latest UK-wide statistics show a
OL,16,F2.1% increase on the number registered
OL,17,Fin 2023 and is the highest number
OL,18,Fsince records began in 1993.
