OL,6,FThe statistics body also said figures
OL,7,Ffor drug misuse and for specific
OL,8,Fsubstances are undercounts because in
OL,9,Faround a fifth of cases, no
OL,10,Finformation is provided about the
OL,11,Fspecific drug or drugs involved on a
OL,12,Fdeath registration form.
OL,14,FIt added that because of delays,
OL,15,Faround half of the deaths registered
OL,16,Fin 2024 will have occurred in previous
OL,17,Fyears.
