OL,6,FDavid Mais, from the ONS, said: "We
OL,7,Fare seeing a small but continued
OL,8,Fincrease in the rate of deaths
OL,9,Frelating to drug poisoning, with
OL,10,Fopioids and opiates, such as heroin
OL,11,Fand morphine, the drugs most commonly
OL,12,Fmentioned on death registrations.
OL,14,F"However, in a fifth of cases, no
OL,15,Finformation is provided about the
OL,16,Fspecific drug or drugs involved.
