OL,6,F"The more information coroners can
OL,7,Fprovide on registrations, the more
OL,8,Fdetailed our analysis can be of the
OL,9,Fsubstances most associated with drug
OL,10,Fpoisoning deaths."
OL,12,FDeaths linked to cocaine were up 14.4%
OL,13,Fon the previous year, with 1,279
OL,14,Fregistered in 2024.
OL,16,FThe ONS said cocaine remained the
OL,17,Fsecond-most used drug after cannabis
OL,18,Fin England and Wales over the past
OL,19,Fdecade.
