OL,6,FMore than three-quarters of cocaine-
OL,7,Flinked deaths registered in 2024 were
OL,8,Fin males ` 982 compared with 297
OL,9,Ffemale deaths.
OL,11,FHeroin and morphine, which the ONS
OL,12,Fsaid are often indistinguishable in
OL,13,Ftoxicology testing, remained the most
OL,14,Ffrequently mentioned opiates and
OL,15,Fopioids in death registrations.
OL,17,FA total of 1,415 drug poisoning deaths
OL,18,Fmentioned either one of these
OL,19,Fsubstances in registrations in 2024.
