OL,4,Cyear-on-year
OL,6,FOverall, there were 5,129 deaths
OL,7,Frelated to drug poisoning registered
OL,8,Fin England last year, up from 5,053 in
OL,9,F2023.
OL,11,FThere were 417 drug-related deaths
OL,12,Fregistered in Wales, an increase from
OL,13,F377 the previous year.
OL,15,FThe north-east of England continued to
OL,16,Fhave the highest rates of deaths
OL,17,Frelating to drug poisoning (167.6
OL,18,Fdeaths per million people) and drug
OL,19,Fmisuse (107.1 per million) the ONS
OL,20,Fsaid.
