OL,6,FThe East of England had the lowest
OL,7,Frates for drug poisoning and drug
OL,8,Fmisuse ` at 66.3 deaths per million
OL,9,Fpeople and 40.2 per million,
OL,10,Frespectively.
OL,12,FOf the 5,565 registered drug poisoning
OL,13,Fdeaths in 2024, 3,736 were identified
OL,14,Fas drug misuse, meaning the underlying
OL,15,Fcause of death was drug abuse or drug
OL,16,Fdependence and/or the death involved a
OL,17,Fcontrolled substance under the Misuse
OL,18,Fof Drugs Act.
