OL,6,FThe Turning Point charity, which helps
OL,7,Fpeople with substance abuse problems,
OL,8,Fcalled for increased availability of
OL,9,Fmedication to be given in the event of
OL,10,Fopioid overdoses.
OL,12,FChief operating officer Clare Taylor
OL,13,Fsaid: "Synthetic opioids continue to
OL,14,Fflow into the market.
OL,16,F"Lab-produced opioids pose a
OL,17,Fsignificant risk to life due to their
OL,18,Fpotency and this is reflected in the
OL,19,Ffact that deaths related to nitazenes
OL,20,Fhave increased four-fold compared to
OL,21,Fthe previous year.
